('Arya', 'movie', 'Arya, an eccentric young man, falls in love with a girl already in a relationship and believes in "love without expectations." This romantic drama established Allu Arjun''s signature style and dancing prowess while presenting an unconventional love story that became a cultural phenomenon in Telugu cinema.', '2004-05-07', ARRAY['Romance', 'Drama'], 'U', 'Telugu', 165, 'Sukumar', ARRAY['Allu Arjun', 'Anu Mehta'], ARRAY['Amazon Prime'], 'https://youtu.be/9Q1Iq9JQYqY', 'https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w1280/1RU7eOgierTfTiNNQUmd1h5iKFU.jpg', NULL),
('Race Gurram', 'movie', 'A reckless young man teams up with his police officer brother to take down a powerful crime syndicate. This action-comedy showcases Allu Arjun''s impeccable comic timing and dancing skills in a entertaining package of brotherly bonding and high-stakes action.', '2014-04-11', ARRAY['Action', 'Comedy'], 'U', 'Telugu', 165, 'Surender Reddy', ARRAY['Allu Arjun', 'Shaam'], ARRAY['Disney+ Hotstar'], 'https://youtu.be/9Q1Iq9JQYqY', 'https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w1280/4ojbzpHL0wmlnrmlLQGLds6Hwvu.jpg', NULL),
